Filter-BoxString version 0.02
=============================

Use Filter::BoxString to describe multiline strings with ASCII art
style boxes using '+', '-', and '|' characters.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Filter::Simple

